Installation to N900
--------------------

Note: Installing requires shell access to the device and root priviledges!

Required packages:
- python2.5
- python-gtk2
- python-dbus
- python-hildon
- python-gst0.10

Command for a simple installation case:
$ apt-get install python2.5 python-gtk2 python-dbus python-hildon python-gst0.10

After installing the required packages, Proximate can be installed the 
usual way:

./configure --prefix=/usr && ./install.sh

Please note that "install.sh" must be run as root!
